title: InteractionStart
body:
Hey! Thanks for chatting with me!
Is there anything on your mind?

[[Yes|SomethingOnMind]]
[[No|NothingOnMind]]
[[Kind of|SomethingOnMind]]

title: SomethingOnMind
body:
How is it making you feel?

[[Happy!|MakesFeelHappy]]
[[Sad|MakesFeelSad]]
[[Angry|MakesFeelAngry]]
[[Anxious|MakesFeelAnxious]]
[[Nothing really|MakesFeelNothing]]

title: NothingOnMind
body:
Cool! Having a good day so far?

[[Yeah|HavingGoodDay]]
[[Its alright|HavingAlrightDay]]
[[Not really|NotHavingGoodDay]]

title: MakesFeelAngry
body:
That sucks! Its good to release that anger once in a while. Maybe try writing down why it makes you angry?

[[Ok that sounds good|WroteDown]]
[[No, not right now|DidntWriteDown]]

title: HavingGoodDay
body: Thats great! Good days are the best!

title: HavingAlrightDay
body: Cool! Let's make tomorrow even better!

title: NotHavingGoodDay
body: That sucks! Let's make tomorrow a good day!

title: WroteDown
body: Cool! I find writing things down helps me to get them off my chest.

title: DidntWriteDown
body: Thats ok! I usually find that writing things down helps me to get them off my chest.

title: MoodStart
body:
Hey! How are you feeling today?

[[1|Mood1]]
[[2|Mood2]]
[[3|Mood3]]
[[4|Mood4]]
[[5|Mood5]]

title: Mood1
body: That's not good! I'm here for you!

title: Mood2
body: That's not good! I'm here for you!

title: Mood3
body: Woo! Nothing wrong with a 'whatever' day!

title: Mood5
body: Woohoo! I hope you have a great rest of the day!
